title: Donaldson trades words with Kela, benches clear in ALDS (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,166 Donaldson trades words with Kela, benches clear in ALDS (Yahoo Sports) Toronto Blue Jays slugger Josh Donaldson got into a shouting match with Rangers reliever Keone Kela in the 13th inning in Game 2 of the AL Division Series on Friday, causing the benches and benches to briefly empty. It was 4-all when Donaldson hit a deep drive to left field that went foul. Kela walked toward home plate and began trading words with Donaldson.
